  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and cracked black pepper, cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in vegetable stock, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add shio-koji, sea salt, and heavy cream, stir until combined.",
    "Slide salmon fillets into the pot, cover, and simmer for 8 minutes until cooked through.",
    "Remove fillets, flake them into the broth, and stir gently.",
    "Garnish with fresh dill before serving."
